test/e2e/properties.e2e-spec.ts`\n\nTests property endpoints that include favorite-related fields:\n- Line 247: `expect(res.body.data).toHaveProperty('isFavorited');`\n- Line 279: `it('should return isFavorited=false for unauthenticated user', ...)`\n- Line 284: `expect(res.body.data.isFavorited).toBe(false);`\n\n### D. `/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/backend/test/e2e/admin-users.e2e-spec.ts`\n\nTests admin dashboard that includes favorites count:\n- Line 198: `expect(res.body.data.activity).toHaveProperty('totalFavorites');`\n- Line 212: `expect(typeof res.body.data.activity.totalFavorites).toBe('number');`\n- Line 213: `expect(res.body.data.activity.totalFavorites).toBeGreaterThanOrEqual(0);`\n\n---\n\n## 3. MISSING_ENDPOINTS.yaml\n\n**Does NOT exist anywhere in the workspace.** Searched all paths including:\n- `.claude-project/nestfind/status/MISSING_ENDPOINTS.yaml`\n- `.claude-project/status/**/MISSING_ENDPOINTS*`\n- `**/MISSING_ENDPOINTS*` (glob)\n- `.claude-project/status/` (list)\n\nThe file is referenced in the `implement-favorites` agent log as a self-healing mechanism (`If .claude-project/nestfind/status/MISSING_ENDPOINTS.yaml exists AND lists a resource matching favorites, implement those endpoints too`), but it was never created.\n\n**Existing status files under `.claude-project/nestfind/status/`:**\n- `/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/status/PIPELINE_STATUS.md`\n- `/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/status/BACKEND_TESTS_GENERATED.md`\n- `/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/status/DESIGN_STATUS.md`\n- `/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/status/DATABASE_SCHEMA_REPORT.md`\n- `/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/status/INIT_REPORT.md`\n- `/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/status/DESIGN_FULL_GENERATION_REPORT.md`\n- `/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/status/seed.yaml`\n- Various `.blueprint-*.json` files\n\nAlso notably **missing**: `BACKEND_IMPLEMENT_favorites.md` (the report file the implement-favorites node was supposed to generate). The pipeline shows backend phase as \"Pending.\"\n\n---\n\n## 4. Favorite Entity Definition in PROJECT_DATABASE.md\n\n**File:** `/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/docs/PROJECT_DATABASE.md` (lines 217-238)\n\n```markdown\n### Favorite\n\nRepresents a renter saving a property to their favorites. Idempotent — adding a duplicate returns the existing record (API handles this). Composite unique constraint prevents duplicates.\n\n**Table:** `favorites`\n\n| Field | Type | Constraints | Description |\n|-------|------|-------------|-------------|\n| `id` | `uuid` | PK, default: `uuid_generate_v4()` | Inherited from BaseEntity |\n| `user_id` | `uuid` | FK → `users.id`, NOT NULL, ON DELETE CASCADE | The renter who favorited |\n| `property_id` | `uuid` | FK → `properties.id`, NOT NULL, ON DELETE CASCADE | The favorited property |\n| `created_at` | `timestamp` | NOT NULL, default: `now()` | Inherited from BaseEntity |\n\n**Indexes:**\n- `UNIQUE` on `(user_id, property_id)` — prevents duplicate favorites\n- `INDEX` on `user_id`\n- `INDEX` on `property_id`\n\n**Relationships:**\n- `belongsTo` → `User` via `user_id`\n- `belongsTo` → `Property` via `property_id`\n```\n\nThe Favorite is also referenced elsewhere in PROJECT_DATABASE.md:\n- Line 46: `hasMany → Favorite (one user has many favorites)` under User entity\n- Line 140: `hasMany → Favorite (one property is favorited by many users)` under Property entity\n- Lines 333, 337: ERD relationship lines\n- Lines 351-352: Foreign key references in the FK summary table\n- Lines 362, 365: ORM relationship mappings\n- Line 380: Notes that soft delete is NOT enabled on `favorites` (hard delete on unfavorite)\n\n---\n\n## 5. Favorites API Endpoints in PROJECT_API.md\n\n**File:** `/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/docs/PROJECT_API.md` (lines 710-812)\n\n```markdown\n### Favorites\n\n| Method | Path | Description | Auth |\n|--------|------|-------------|------|\n| GET | `/api/favorites` | List current user's favorite properties | User |\n| POST | `/api/favorites/:propertyId` | Add property to favorites | User |\n| DELETE | `/api/favorites/:propertyId` | Remove property from favorites | User |\n\n#### GET /api/favorites\n\nList all favorited properties for the current user.\n\n**Query Parameters:**\n\n| Parameter | Type | Default | Description |\n|-----------|------|---------|-------------|\n| page | number | 1 | Page number (≥1) |\n| limit | number | 20 | Items per page (1–100) |\n\n**Request Body:** None\n\n**Success Response (200):**\n{\n  \"statusCode\": 200,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"items\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"uuid\",\n        \"title\": \"string\",\n        \"price\": 2500.00,\n        \"bedrooms\": 2,\n        \"bathrooms\": 1,\n        \"propertyType\": \"apartment\",\n        \"address\": {\n          \"city\": \"San Francisco\",\n          \"state\": \"CA\"\n        },\n        \"thumbnailUrl\": \"string | null\",\n        \"favoritedAt\": \"ISO 8601 datetime\"\n      }\n    ],\n    \"meta\": {\n      \"total\": 8,\n      \"page\": 1,\n      \"limit\": 20,\n      \"totalPages\": 1\n    }\n  }\n}\n\n**Error Responses:** 401\n\n#### POST /api/favorites/:propertyId\n\nAdd a property to the current user's favorites. Idempotent — if already favorited, returns 200 with existing record.\n\n**Path Parameters:**\n| propertyId | UUID | Property ID |\n\n**Request Body:** None\n\n**Success Response (201):**\n{\n  \"statusCode\": 201,\n  \"message\": \"Property added to favorites\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": \"uuid\",\n    \"userId\": \"uuid\",\n    \"propertyId\": \"uuid\",\n    \"createdAt\": \"ISO 8601 datetime\"\n  }\n}\n\n**Error Responses:** 400 (validation), 401, 404 (property not found)\n\n#### DELETE /api/favorites/:propertyId\n\nRemove a property from favorites.\n\n**Path Parameters:**\n| propertyId | UUID | Property ID |\n\n**Request Body:** None\n\n**Success Response (204):** No body\n\n**Error Responses:** 401, 404 (not in favorites)\n```\n\n**Important discrepancy between API spec and E2E tests:**\n- The API spec says `POST /api/favorites/:propertyId` and `DELETE /api/favorites/:propertyId` (propertyId in the URL path)\n- The E2E tests call `POST /api/favorites` with `{ propertyId: property1.id }` as a body parameter, and `DELETE /api/favorites/${property1.id}`\n- The E2E tests expect `DELETE` to return 200 (not 204 as in the spec), and `POST` was tested with missing `propertyId` in the body (not as a path param)\n\nThe tests, the entity, the migration, and the PROJECT_API.md have **consistent intent** but the API spec and test files diverge on the `POST` path format.\n\n---\n\n## 6. Relevant Enums\n\n### Backend enums:\nAll under `/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/backend/src/common/enums/`:\n\n| File | Enum | Values | Relevance to Favorites |\n|------|------|--------|------------------------|\n| `role.enum.ts` | `RoleEnum` | `RENTER = 'renter'`, `ADMIN = 'admin'` | Auth guard for favorites: renter-only access |\n| `user-status.enum.ts` | `UserStatusEnum` | `ACTIVE = 'active'`, `SUSPENDED = 'suspended'` | Suspended users should be blocked from favorites |\n| `property-type.enum.ts` | `PropertyTypeEnum` | `APARTMENT, HOUSE, CONDO, TOWNHOUSE, STUDIO` | Property type appears in favorited property response |\n| `inquiry-status.enum.ts` | `InquiryStatusEnum` | `NEW, READ, RESPONDED` | Not directly related to favorites |\n\n### Frontend enums:\n**No frontend files exist at all.** The `frontend/app/` directory is empty — the frontend has not been scaffolded yet.\n\n---\n\n## 7. Additional Related Files\n\n### Migration file: `/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/backend/src/database/migrations/00